# High level Validation flow

For a random subset of active miners ( where active miners are miners with recent gradients)  : 

-  run a forward pass on the miner data on its model
- merges the miners gradient into its model .

- Gather Binary indicator in an EMA (its a coarse signal; correct most of the times not all).
- Gradient Score = % improvement on Random data.
- Gradient Score Ema 
- Final Score : weighted MA of Binary EMA and Gradient Score EMA
